{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "16.0",
      "line_index": 16,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c7e580f4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う……うぅ、身体、熱い……はぁ……はーっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "19.0",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d129846f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "夕食後、気分が優れずベッドに横になって休んでいた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.0",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "40a5ff4d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかし気分が改善するどころか、どんどん身体が熱を帯び、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.2",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "40a5ff4d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "全身から汗が噴き出し動悸が激しくなっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4d5f7a51",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（そういえばリリアン達が妙にお代わりを薦めてきていたな……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.2",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4d5f7a51",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "まさか夕飯に何か入っていた……？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "27e583c5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（い、いや、疑うのは良くない……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.2",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "27e583c5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いつも作ってくれているわけだし、きっと原因はほかに……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "38a7ce76",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ううう……！　ぐ……うあ、あああ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.0",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d3c97af7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "睾丸が急に疼き出し、思わず声が出てしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "158a3258",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "先ほどまでの全身の熱が下半身の一点のみに集中する、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.2",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "158a3258",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな感覚に襲われる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.0",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86f71691",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──トントン",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.0",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "709a36af",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ねぇ……部屋入ってもいい？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.0",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e3843e49",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハル……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.0",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2f17906",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "聞き慣れた声に少し安堵を覚える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.0",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cb3b8092",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "入って、と声を振り絞るとドアがガチャリと開く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.0",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d5cb3777",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ねぇ、あんたさっき様子が……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.3",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "d5cb3777",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "って！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.5",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 5,
      "line_hash": "d5cb3777",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ちょ、ちょっと……！？　だいじょうぶ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.0",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9d250b12",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "顔が汗まみれの俺の様子に驚いたのか、慌てて駆け寄るコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.0",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b85fd7fe",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "慌ててハンカチを取り出すと、俺の顔を拭き始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.0",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "58438f75",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "な、何があったの？　どうしてこんな……すごい汗じゃない",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.0",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cb0776a0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "わ、わかんないんだ……身体が、下半身が熱くて……うう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.0",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d21cff0d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "下半身……って！？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.2",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d21cff0d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "こ、これ……ちょ、ちょっとお布団めくるわよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.0",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bbd1879f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "──っっっ！？！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.0",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e1d8e24b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは布団をめくると、声にならない声をあげる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "82.0",
      "line_index": 82,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ca81d2c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなコハルの声に釣られるように視線を下半身に向ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.0",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cffcfe88",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──んなぁ！？　な、なんじゃこりゃ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.0",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f0232ff6",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そ、そんなのあたしが聞きたいわよ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.0",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e61415d5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ズボンの上からもはっきりわかるほど、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.2",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e61415d5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒がギンギンに勃起してまっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.0",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "90c59901",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな俺の様子に赤面するコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.0",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b95119c6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "じっと俺の下半身を見つめ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.2",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b95119c6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "見られていることにさらに下半身が熱くなってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "99.0",
      "line_index": 99,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "94821853",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "なんで……あんた何かヘンなこと考えていないわよねっ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.0",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "909cf046",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そんなわけねーだろ……考える余裕なんてぇ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.0",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "96beacd5",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "だったら原因はほかに……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.4",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "96beacd5",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ううん、今はそんなことを考えている余裕はないよね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.0",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3cb3aa04",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "<size=18>ほかの子もしてるんだし、あ、あたしだって……</size>",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.0",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1aed1579",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "その……あ、あたしが何とかしてあげるから……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "120.0",
      "line_index": 120,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "901c8772",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──えっ？　あ、ちょ……！？　コハル！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "125.0",
      "line_index": 125,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3161c804",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは俺のベルトを外すと、ズボンを脱がせ始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9e667346",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思わぬコハルの行動にやめさせようとするも、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.2",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9e667346",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは何かを決意したかのようにパンツも脱がしてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.0",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9cd52d4c",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "だ、だいじょうぶだから……あたし、その、いちおーは知ってるから……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.3",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "9cd52d4c",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "だからじっとしてて……すぐに元に戻してあげるから……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.0",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ab74d547",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う、あ……！　コハル……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.0",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2e1f408d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "すごく熱い……あたし、今からこんなおっきいのを……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "150.0",
      "line_index": 150,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "812089bc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは俺だけが恥ずかしくならないようにと自身も衣服を脱ぐ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.0",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dd194cad",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルが何をしているのかここからは見えないが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.2",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "dd194cad",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒が柔らかなモノに包まれ、それがコハルの胸であることは",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.4",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "dd194cad",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "瞬時に理解できた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.0",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ca4a0adb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（コハルのあそこ……丸見え……お尻の穴まで……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.0",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d214781e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "子供の頃、コハルとは日常的に近い形でお風呂に一緒に入っていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5a3adac8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だから裸は結構見慣れていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.0",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "13e1302f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでもあそこもお尻の穴もこんなに近くで見たことはない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.0",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3728d291",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "幼馴染の初めて見せるエッチなところが俺をさらに高ぶらせ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.2",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3728d291",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒に痛みが走るほど、さらに大きく勃起してしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "166.0",
      "line_index": 166,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3eb541df",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（コハル、いつのまにこんなにむっちりして……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "170.0",
      "line_index": 170,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4bdee37b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "きゃうっ！？♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "170.2",
      "line_index": 170,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4bdee37b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ちょ、ちょっとぉ……そんなに太もも撫でないでぇ……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "173.0",
      "line_index": 173,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "77c0d002",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "す、すまん……！　つい……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.0",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f3df4b6a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あんたの……子供の頃のと全然違ってるね……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.2",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f3df4b6a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "何だかすごく大人って感じになっちゃってる……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.0",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f713c612",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "熱くて硬くて……でもココはふにゃって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.2",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f713c612",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あ、なんかふにふにして意外に揉み心地がいいかも……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "183.0",
      "line_index": 183,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f9d1f53b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "イ゛っ！？　お、おい！　そこそんなに強く揉むなって……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.0",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1eb6fceb",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ふえぇっ！？　あ、ご、ごめん……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.2",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1eb6fceb",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ど、どのくらいが気持ち良いのかわかんなかったから……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.0",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "49b0c92e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、そ、その……す、すまん……つい声出してしまって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.2",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "49b0c92e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "その……優しくしてくれれば……最初に触ったみたいに……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "194.0",
      "line_index": 194,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1c40e6f0",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そう、なんだ……うん、わかった♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "194.2",
      "line_index": 194,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1c40e6f0",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "いっぱい優しく揉んであげるから……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.0",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9bce777d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは優しく、そして丁寧に睾丸を揉み、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.2",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9bce777d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゾクゾクした快感に腰が震える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "199.0",
      "line_index": 199,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "22426ff",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（ああ……なんかコハルに流されるままにしちゃってるな……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "199.2",
      "line_index": 199,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "22426ff",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "でもこんなの拒否なんてできっこない……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "202.0",
      "line_index": 202,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fa3d9a97",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルのぴったりと閉じた割れ目を見つめながらそんなことを思う。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "204.0",
      "line_index": 204,
      "inline_index": 0,
