      "line_hash": "ca239284",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "──ひぃっ！？♥　あっ！♥　いやぁっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "361.2",
      "line_index": 361,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ca239284",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そこお尻の……あああぁっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "363.0",
      "line_index": 363,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6c6f8d6e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ひくひくと蠢いたピンク色のアナルにそっと指で触れる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "364.0",
      "line_index": 364,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3089a4d1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少し指を差し込むだけで腰が大きく跳ね、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "364.2",
      "line_index": 364,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3089a4d1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "大量の愛液が膣穴から噴き出す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "367.0",
      "line_index": 367,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aed14e32",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ううう！♥　この、ヘンタイぃっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "367.2",
      "line_index": 367,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "aed14e32",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "女の子のそんなところ触るなんてぇ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "370.0",
      "line_index": 370,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "95c0432b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハルだって同じだろっ。普通男のタマなんて触らないって",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "374.0",
      "line_index": 374,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4498e942",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ひゃううっ！♥　これは、あんたを少しでも……感じさせたいからでぇ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "377.0",
      "line_index": 377,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2fa3859",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺だって同じだ……コハルに少しでも気持ち良くなってほしいからっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "381.0",
      "line_index": 381,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d0cd0ea8",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あ、ああああ……！！♥　お豆ダメぇ！　ひああああぁっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "383.0",
      "line_index": 383,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "862efd82",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぷっくりと大きくなっていたクリトリスを舌先で触れると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "383.2",
      "line_index": 383,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "862efd82",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルの身体がビクンビクンと跳ねあがる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "386.0",
      "line_index": 386,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "100a07a1",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ダメっ！♥　ダメっ！♥　そんなにされたら、あたしぃぃっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "386.2",
      "line_index": 386,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "100a07a1",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あたしだけイクのイヤ……あんたも、あんたも一緒にぃぃっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "389.0",
      "line_index": 389,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "396fee51",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ああ、わかってる……！　またコハルにぶっかけるから……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "389.2",
      "line_index": 389,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "396fee51",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺の精液で真っ白に汚すから……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "393.0",
      "line_index": 393,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ba6b4110",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ふあああぁっ！♥　あああぁっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "393.2",
      "line_index": 393,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ba6b4110",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "クリ気持ち良いっ！！♥もうダメ……！♥　クる、キちゃうっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "393.4",
      "line_index": 393,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "ba6b4110",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "波が迫ってくるぅぅっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "396.0",
      "line_index": 396,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2061ce40",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハル……うう、また出るっ！！　う、くうううっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "408.0",
      "line_index": 408,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "63cbd5b6",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "んああぁぁっ！♥　あぁぁっ！♥　ふあああぁぁぁぁ～～っ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "410.0",
      "line_index": 410,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c9691f1d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺達は同時に絶頂し、コハルの尿道から大量の潮が噴き出す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "411.0",
      "line_index": 411,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f72c9822",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "びちゃびちゃとそれが顔にかかり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "411.2",
      "line_index": 411,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f72c9822",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルがイってくれたことに喜びを覚える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "414.0",
      "line_index": 414,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "439a82f5",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "う、あ……♥　ああ、さっきよりいっぱい……♥　しゅごいぃ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "414.2",
      "line_index": 414,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "439a82f5",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ああ……この匂い、好きぃ……はぁぁっ♥　ああああぁ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "416.0",
      "line_index": 416,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5b118c02",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは射精を求め睾丸を揉み続け、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "416.2",
      "line_index": 416,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5b118c02",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "押し出されるように何度も熱いモノが駆け上がる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "418.0",
      "line_index": 418,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1dc77d5f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すべてを搾り取られたような快感に、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "418.2",
      "line_index": 418,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1dc77d5f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "腰が何度も痙攣してしまっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "421.0",
      "line_index": 421,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ddd2abfb",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うう……ばかぁ……♥　あたしまでイかせることないのにぃ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "424.0",
      "line_index": 424,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1779346",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "目の前にコハルのおまんこがあったら舐めたくなるって。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "424.2",
      "line_index": 424,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1779346",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それにコハルのイクところが見られて最高に興奮できた",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "428.0",
      "line_index": 428,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4739ccb8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もう俺達は子供の頃と違うって、それがはっきり認識できたし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "432.0",
      "line_index": 432,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "34b7d0c",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うん……そうだね……♥　もうあたし達はただの幼馴染じゃないよね……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "435.0",
      "line_index": 435,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2c798c11",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あんたもさっきよりもいっぱい射精してくれて嬉しい……♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "435.2",
      "line_index": 435,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2c798c11",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "またエッチな気分になったらさ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "435.4",
      "line_index": 435,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "2c798c11",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "その、ほかの子じゃなくてあたしを頼ってよ？♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "438.0",
      "line_index": 438,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7cfcc1fb",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あんたを一番知っているあたしが",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "438.2",
      "line_index": 438,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7cfcc1fb",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "いっぱい気持ち良くしてあげるから♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "442.0",
      "line_index": 442,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "361889f7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……わかった",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "446.0",
      "line_index": 446,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1d52fba9",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ふふっ♥　約束だからね？♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "446.2",
      "line_index": 446,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1d52fba9",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "もうあんたの目にはあたししか入らないようにしてやるんだから♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "449.0",
      "line_index": 449,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9f1c8890",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "──ちゅっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "451.0",
      "line_index": 451,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bc670840",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは嬉しそうにそう言うと、亀頭にキスをする。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "453.0",
      "line_index": 453,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5d814007",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなコハルの可愛さに、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "453.2",
      "line_index": 453,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5d814007",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハル以外の子が本当に目に入らくなるかもしれない、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "454.0",
      "line_index": 454,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c13a595",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そう思ってしまうのであった。",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
